                    </div>
                    <span>If you're writing a Java compiler or Java Virtual Machine, this book is a must-have. It's also great for the serious Java programmer who is interested in the "guts" of how Java works. But if you want a tutorial on the JVM, you'll be better served by another book. Before you  buy this book, you should also know that the on-line version is freely  available.</span>
                  
